Im going to copy / paste my latest text to Melissa as of this morning. Youll have more context before we speak. But you wont have all the context. So i will speak to you once youve read it. Let me know when youre ready

I hear you. Ive listened to what little youve shared. I should abide by that. And i will. 

I was kindly asked that you be left alone. So, as difficult as that is, im honoring that. I won't be coming home tonight. Or any time in the future.

Your desire to find your own place and for our money to fund two places isn't necessary if i leave. Its no longer a burden. You dont have to endure that of moving out, moving in somewhere else, then only to quickly move again back to Philly  

You are focused now on just you. I wanted that. Im accepting it and getting in your way is all i am doing simply be being, and existing in the same home as you. 

Since im not in your current equation or focus, there is no room in that equation for you, or i needing to know each others  location. Those alerts, coming and going and having that visibility doesnt align with your ask of me. So i removed my location permission from the life360 app. Please do the same.

You have no more responsibilities to burden you. I am not kidnapping Lucy. I want that to be known. Lucy is part of the ‚Äúus‚Äù equation. It cant be part of the on focusing on you equation.

Im focusing on us, that includes me, but also includes you, and that included us, all three of us. In my mind, every day in the past and every day moving forward will be consumed with that focus, and to allow you the space you kindly asked me to provide you. 

The lease is paid in full now. You have that house until August 31st to use as you please. It's yours. I won't be coming back. Everything there is yours to keep, sell, or take with you. I only took what i needed to live and what lucy needed to live. Lucy is ours. She's focused on us forever. ‚ÄúUs‚Äù is one person to her. For me, ‚Äúus‚Äù is collectively the three of us 
me + you + lucy. Thats the equation im focused on. With only love. 

If you need to talk to me for whatever reason im going to make myself available. If you cant reach me, say my phone is off or not next to me, there only a few places ill be in that moment. So you know where to find me, you know how to reach me, you know what im doing, and you have a good idea of where i am. Im available to you, just speak up. Until then, im going to hold my word. You have the space and i hopefully less a burden with me, without us, and a place to rest and plan whats next, whats best, for you. 

I texted barb. I want you to know that before i speak to her. Shes your sister and shes a great one to have. Im going to tell her what i see and feel. My concerns for you. Thank you for offering me the your blessing in doing that. I will not be calling Sherry, your dad, mary, or anyone else. I will hand over my love for you to barb as i trust her completely. You may join me at 4:45 at Marks to listen only if you want to. Im not requiring any commitment from you, especially one day later after you asked for space and shared the news that you wanted to not live in the same home as me, as us, and to do so for you. I will not leave out what my role is in this to barb, i will not present myself to be a victim. I am responsible for my role in this. But i can no longer support what you need. I have check. It was dated for yesterday but if you cash it, it will bounce. Ive sold pretty much every last investment to prepare it in an account that will be visible and available to you. Venmo has a cap in terms of how much i can send at once. If you need any amount immediately, i will venmo you as much as i can today. Our money is your money. I won't be a gatekeeper to our money if your telling me you need it for the benefit of your immediate well being

And the jeep is yours to keep indefinitely. Whether you drive it home to philly, or leave it wherever, you can consider it yours. If i have to transfer the title to you so you can register it in your name, i will draft up a bill of sale and label it a gift so you dont incur PA sales tax and you can then register/insure in your name
I have to run an errand. Maybe around Noon? Im sorry barb

Just wanted to say thank you. Thank you for being direct. Thank you for being there for Melissa all these months. Thank you for being there for me when i needed specifically you, who i consider my sister. I love you barb. 

We had a really hard conversation last night that could have, likely would have/should have, ended us for good...but we survived it. 

We had a small breakthrough last night. Small, but just barely large enough to possibly be the return of something, if nothing else, the return of hope, and the resurfacing of love. For me, and for Melissa, the return of want - the wanting of making it, returning to us.

Had i not talked to you when i did i don't believe we would have survived it. 

Today felt like a date at the dog beach. I got a kiss in the water, with us holding lucy together, that snapped me back into seeing Melissa as the beautiful person that never went anywhere to begin with. 

I love you Barb. Thank you
